creator: Onestepwin
descriptionHtml:
💰 StepWin is a free pedometer that can track the steps you walked and the calories you burned every day. No paid feature or subscription, it's all free! It can help you keep fit and rewards your move. It converts your steps into “coin” for amazing bonus.

🙌 How to earn coin?
1. Download & open StepWin pedometer, it counts your steps automatically. No login!
2. Rewards your Walk. Your steps can be exchanged for gold coins. Tap the coin jumping on the step counter to collect it .
3. You can also earn cash and gold coins by playing games and watching videos, and make a lot of money without leaving home.

🏆 Free & Easy-to-use Pedometer App
No login, no personal information! As long as you download this app, it will automatically record your steps regardless of whether your phone is locked or turned on.

🔒 Safe & Save Power
This step counter uses the built-in sensor to count your steps. No GPS tracking, so it barely consumes battery power.

StepWin is the fun and profitable pedometer that will motivate you to walk or run more every day!

Get communication with us as you meet any problem at once!

💰 StepWin is a free pedometer that can track the steps you walked and the calories you burned every day. No paid feature or subscription, it's all free! As an one-tap tools to build health and fitness habits and beat weight loss goals, it can help you keep fit and motivate you to get move.

🥇 Weight loss, BMI tracking and calorie burn counter
-Track your Health and Fitness Data. Create Healthy Habits.
-Reach your goal: Walk more, Lose weight, or Improve health!

🏆 Free & Easy-to-use Pedometer App
The best pedometer for any phone. No login, no personal information! As long as you download this app, it will automatically record your steps regardless of whether your phone is locked or turned on.

🔒 Safe & Save Power
This step counter uses the built-in sensor to count your steps. No GPS tracking, so it barely consumes battery power.

StepWin is a fun and motivated pedometer that will motivate you to walk or run more every day! Make every step count and lose more weight.

🙌 Download the Pedometer app for free to turn your phone into your personal health and weight loss tracker! Lose weight with calorie burning guided fitness plans, step counting and activity tracking. Join us and get fit and active!

🥇 Weight loss, BMI tracking and calorie burn counter
-Track your Health and Fitness Data. Create Healthy Habits.
-Reach your goal: Walk more, Lose weight, or Improve health!
-Track your steps, activity and calorie burn.

🏆 Free & Easy-to-use Pedometer App
The best pedometer for any phone. No login, no personal information! As long as you download this app, it will automatically record your steps regardless of whether your phone is locked or turned on.

🔒 Safe & Save Power
This step counter uses the built-in sensor to count your steps. No GPS tracking, so it barely consumes battery power.

StepWin is a fun and motivated pedometer that will motivate you to walk or run more every day! Make every step count and lose more weight.
